INSPIRATION

bkit-doctor was inspired by bkit, an AI-native development workflow toolkit.

The phase-based workflow methodology, the Plan → Design → Do → Check structure,
and the concept of structured AI collaboration used in this project were
influenced by the ideas presented in bkit's introductory materials.

bkit is NOT included in this project.
